title: Package Receiving, Central Air Conditioning, Island Kitchen.
posting_body: Find the right house for you, whether you need a work-from-home area or a peaceful private courtyard patio to enjoy the fresh air with your morning coffee.
You're in the Lower Queen Anne area, which gives you easy access to the lively city life of Seattle's central center.
Chef's kitchens with stainless steel appliances and quartz countertops are available in our pet-friendly rental houses.
An in-unit washer and dryer, floor-to-ceiling windows, hard-plank flooring, and luxurious carpeting are among the other amenities.
A gorgeous rooftop terrace with grilling stations and a fire pit promises the greatest views of Elliot Bay in Seattle, as well as a resident lounge, a fitness facility, and inside bike storage.
Our neighborhood is less than two miles from some of Seattle's major companies, including Amazon, Google, Starbucks, the Gates Foundation, Expedia, and the University of Washington.
Take advantage of the adjacent I-5 highway and hit the road when adventure calls.
-Bark Park and NEW Indoor Pet Grooming Spa!
